      <title>日本央行前官員預測日本將繼續幹預以防止日圓暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/ex-boj-official-predicts-japan-will-keep-intervening-prevent-yen-free-fall-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位十年前參與東京市場進軍的前央行官員表示，日本可能會繼續幹預以支撐日圓，直到投機者引發日圓大幅貶值的風險被消除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/ex-boj-official-predicts-japan-will-keep-intervening-prevent-yen-free-fall-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
