      <title>歐洲股市在財報潮中開盤下跌，聯準會結果</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-open-earnings-tide-fed-outcome-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[歐洲股市週四開盤低迷，因投資人在周中假期後回歸，分析大量大額財報，且聯準會暗示將延後降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-open-earnings-tide-fed-outcome-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:33:31 GMT</pubDate>
